  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this phase II study is to determine the efficacy of fenretinide in the
      treatment of geographic atrophy (GA) in subjects with the dry form of age-related macular
      degeneration (AMD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
